WEBVTT

00:39.020 --> 00:40.360
May I be like the stars

00:40.380 --> 00:41.580
and you like the moon.

00:42.450 --> 00:43.670
As long as the world remains,

00:44.780 --> 00:45.780
so shall we.

01:01.720 --> 01:03.830
I only wish to stay with the one I love,

01:04.430 --> 01:06.060
watching every sunrise and sunset.

01:07.640 --> 01:09.370
I want to be with you forever.

01:13.620 --> 01:14.920
Eternals and demons walk different paths.

01:15.640 --> 01:17.480
You and she are ultimately different.

01:37.970 --> 01:39.600
Have you ever

01:40.220 --> 01:41.789
truly cared for me?

01:44.440 --> 01:45.250
No.

01:45.660 --> 01:46.360
Never.

01:54.650 --> 01:57.720
In this life and the next, through all lifetimes…

02:02.150 --> 02:03.310
May we live and die together,

02:04.400 --> 02:06.040
and share life and death as one.

02:41.710 --> 02:45.710
[Moonlight Mystique]

02:46.340 --> 02:49.990
[Episode 6]

02:55.520 --> 02:56.470
Without me,

02:57.360 --> 02:58.360
the Desireless Stone

02:58.360 --> 03:00.000
is useless to you.

03:00.000 --> 03:01.750
Since it's in my body,

03:01.750 --> 03:03.280
I have the final say

03:03.800 --> 03:04.960
who it belongs to.

03:05.430 --> 03:06.840
Your acting is pretty good.

03:11.640 --> 03:12.830
Bai Shuo.

03:12.880 --> 03:14.530
You know clearly that

03:15.260 --> 03:17.020
I need you to gather the Contemplations

03:17.050 --> 03:18.820
and activate the Desireless Stone.

03:18.870 --> 03:21.120
Not only will I not kill you, but I'll also protect you.

03:21.290 --> 03:22.490
However, the Eternals

03:22.520 --> 03:24.780
will only try to kill you to retrieve the Desireless Stone

03:24.810 --> 03:27.180
or lock you up with the Desireless Stone

03:27.200 --> 03:29.670
for the so-called "bigger picture."

03:29.700 --> 03:31.910
So it might seem that I took you away with me,

03:31.930 --> 03:34.280
but in fact, you voluntarily followed me.

03:34.310 --> 03:35.690
Am I right?

03:36.750 --> 03:38.520
Bai Xun was killed by the Demon Race.

03:38.540 --> 03:39.940
I know you want to become stronger

03:39.970 --> 03:41.250
and seek revenge,

03:41.270 --> 03:42.640
but you can't count on the Human Race.

03:42.700 --> 03:44.670
You can only choose between the Eternal Race and the Demon Race.

03:45.220 --> 03:47.310
You've seen the incompetence of the Eternal Race.

03:47.340 --> 03:49.250
The Eternal Race is not your first choice.

03:49.960 --> 03:51.280
You know very well that

03:51.300 --> 03:52.700
only the Bright Moon Palace

03:52.730 --> 03:54.860
can truly help you.

03:55.000 --> 03:57.800
But you wouldn't admit defeat to me.

03:57.850 --> 03:59.610
Now that I brought you back,

03:59.730 --> 04:02.010
I've given you an excuse to save face,

04:02.590 --> 04:03.740
right?

04:05.520 --> 04:06.960
Don't be so conceited.

04:07.470 --> 04:08.360
Without the Bright Moon Palace,

04:08.360 --> 04:10.910
I can still kill Zhen Yu and Fu Ling.

04:12.420 --> 04:13.550
Good.

04:13.750 --> 04:16.640
I like the way you act tough.

04:19.950 --> 04:21.829
Don't you want to seek revenge on your own?

04:22.290 --> 04:23.510
Come on.

04:23.550 --> 04:25.350
I'll stand right here

04:25.510 --> 04:27.080
and won't move a step.

04:27.240 --> 04:29.720
If you could do me even the slightest harm,

04:29.740 --> 04:31.630
I'll let you go immediately,

04:31.660 --> 04:33.810
and I won't ask about the Desireless Stone anymore.

04:39.560 --> 04:41.200
You said it yourself.

04:48.480 --> 04:49.360
Again.

05:06.860 --> 05:08.390
Do you think us Three Kings of the Demon Race

05:08.390 --> 05:09.630
got our title for nothing?

05:09.920 --> 05:12.040
Zhen Yu is no weaker than me.

05:12.080 --> 05:13.630
You can't even get close to me,

05:13.630 --> 05:15.040
yet you dream about killing him?

05:15.040 --> 05:16.660
Your mediocre skills

05:16.680 --> 05:19.300
may be more than enough to fight among the Human Race,

05:19.390 --> 05:21.480
but in the face of absolute power,

05:21.510 --> 05:22.780
you are nothing.

05:22.870 --> 05:26.100
♫Crossing the abyss to fulfill our vow♫

05:26.520 --> 05:30.010
♫I'll leap without a thought for tomorrow♫

05:30.330 --> 05:32.830
♫This moment feels like forever♫

05:31.880 --> 05:33.360
Your resistance now

05:33.200 --> 05:36.050
♫I've missed too much time in my life♫

05:33.380 --> 05:35.330
is just an outlet for your emotions.

05:36.210 --> 05:40.070
♫I'll throw myself into this flame for you♫

05:36.480 --> 05:38.390
You don't have any choice anymore.

05:38.409 --> 05:39.400
Bai Shuo.

05:40.670 --> 05:42.190
♫Even if I'll perish♫

05:42.580 --> 05:45.220
♫At lease I can still kiss your face♫

05:45.460 --> 05:48.250
♫Burn out my waning moon♫

05:48.680 --> 05:57.060
♫In exchange for a lifetime of passion♫

05:52.620 --> 05:53.890
You're considered smart

05:53.950 --> 05:55.310
among humans.

05:55.310 --> 05:56.390
Although you wouldn't admit

05:56.390 --> 05:58.200
what I said just now is true,

05:58.250 --> 05:59.810
you know very well that

05:59.830 --> 06:01.830
only when you become strong enough to intimidate your opponent

06:02.280 --> 06:03.980
can your revenge begin.

06:07.040 --> 06:09.200
What if I want to kill you too?

06:12.180 --> 06:13.440
As long as you can.

06:25.510 --> 06:26.480
You've got something to say?

06:26.920 --> 06:28.510
Why did you do that, Master?

06:28.670 --> 06:30.790
I just don't want her to run around with the Desireless Stone.

06:30.820 --> 06:32.060
If it's just to control her,

06:32.110 --> 06:33.580
there are many ways.

06:33.610 --> 06:35.280
Why did you choose the most troublesome one?

06:36.260 --> 06:37.330
What are you trying to say?

06:37.360 --> 06:38.760
I just want to remind you, Master,

06:38.780 --> 06:41.480
not to be swayed by some momentary compassion.

06:41.610 --> 06:44.010
There are only three stars left on the Seven Stars Soul Burning Seal.

06:44.040 --> 06:46.760
If the stars are all gone, even if Bai Shuo doesn't kill you,

06:46.810 --> 06:48.930
there will be no Master of the Bright Moon Palace in the world anymore.

06:48.950 --> 06:50.630
I know what I'm doing.

06:51.380 --> 06:53.430
She's a human who broke into the fight between Eternals and demons.

06:53.620 --> 06:55.380
She must learn the abilities to protect herself.

06:55.870 --> 06:58.070
Otherwise, how can she be my ally?

07:04.080 --> 07:05.990
Bai Shuo can activate the Desireless Stone?

07:06.650 --> 07:07.770
Sect Leader.

07:07.870 --> 07:08.870
Please allow me

07:08.870 --> 07:10.750
to lead troops to the Polar Region to bring Bai Shuo back.

07:10.750 --> 07:13.190
Of course we must retrieve the Desireless Stone.

07:13.190 --> 07:16.120
It's just the Polar Region stretches for hundreds of thousands of miles.

07:16.720 --> 07:20.350
To this day, no one knows where the Bright Moon Palace is.

07:20.480 --> 07:22.510
We can only send disciples

07:22.530 --> 07:24.880
to locate the Bright Moon Palace first.

07:25.370 --> 07:26.690
Once they find it,

07:26.830 --> 07:29.160
they'll bring Bai Shuo back.

07:30.430 --> 07:31.830
I thought you

07:31.830 --> 07:33.570
went to negotiate with Fan Yue, Sect Leader.

07:34.120 --> 07:36.390
When you came back, you even said Fan Yue was nice,

07:36.390 --> 07:38.690
and that he would let Bai Shuo make her own choice.

07:38.790 --> 07:39.590
But look what happened. Where is she?

07:39.620 --> 07:42.550
Who can help me out here?

07:44.710 --> 07:46.320
The Demon Race is fickle

07:46.360 --> 07:47.270
and has no moral principles.

07:47.300 --> 07:49.370
This is not something Sect Leader could have predicted.

07:50.600 --> 07:51.310
Sect Leader.

07:51.600 --> 07:52.430
Where is Chong Zhao?

07:52.430 --> 07:53.920
Why haven't I seen him since he came back?

07:53.920 --> 07:55.310
He knew he was at fault,

07:55.310 --> 07:57.750
and he petitioned for a self-imposed punishment of 300 Red Bone Whips.

07:58.050 --> 07:59.570
300 Red Bone Whips?

08:04.080 --> 08:06.550
The Red Bone Whip is Lanling's punishment for felonies.

08:06.630 --> 08:07.630
Every whip will hurt the bone.

08:08.030 --> 08:09.590
It may seem to cause physical injuries,

08:09.610 --> 08:11.540
but it actually tortures the soul.

08:25.070 --> 08:26.440
Since you can't bear to see him like that, Sect Leader,

08:26.460 --> 08:28.170
why did you agree to his petition

08:28.200 --> 08:29.560
and let him be punished so heavily?

08:29.580 --> 08:31.730
He should be punished for his mistake.

08:31.750 --> 08:34.190
He cannot be let off the hook for the chaos he brought to Ning'an.

08:34.220 --> 08:36.030
Besides the 300 Red Bone Whips,

08:36.049 --> 08:38.200
he also needs to reflect on his mistakes at the Heart-guarding Cliff.

08:38.789 --> 08:40.320
That being said,

08:40.320 --> 08:42.890
the real sinner is the Cold Spring Palace.

08:42.970 --> 08:45.810
The Cold Spring Palace violated the iron law between Eternals and demons

08:45.840 --> 08:48.450
and harmed the Human Race. Of course it should be executed.

08:49.470 --> 08:50.470
Yan Huo.

08:51.120 --> 08:53.430
Send a letter to the 72 Sects

08:53.450 --> 08:55.340
and invite all Sect Leaders here

08:55.370 --> 08:57.650
to discuss the crusade against the Cold Spring Palace.

08:57.670 --> 08:58.620
Yes.

08:59.650 --> 09:00.410
Go.

09:03.880 --> 09:04.850
Now,

09:04.880 --> 09:07.390
the Desireless Stone has been brought to the Bright Moon Palace by Fan Yue.

09:07.410 --> 09:09.290
It won't be easy if we want to take it by force.

09:09.320 --> 09:12.250
Then it depends on whether my beloved disciple, Fu Ling,

09:12.310 --> 09:15.230
can make Chong Zhao defect or not.

09:15.840 --> 09:17.720
Grand Master, so you want to take advantage of Chong Zhao's relationship

09:17.740 --> 09:19.170
with Bai Shuo?

09:20.320 --> 09:22.160
Before he dies,

09:22.180 --> 09:23.220
if

09:23.250 --> 09:24.850
he can really

09:24.870 --> 09:26.820
lure out Bai Shuo and the Desireless Stone for me,

09:28.010 --> 09:29.370
that will be

09:29.510 --> 09:31.240
his last glory.

09:41.260 --> 09:42.530
I'll choose

09:42.610 --> 09:44.010
my own path.

09:44.040 --> 09:46.330
No one has the right to make decisions for me.

09:53.040 --> 09:53.990
Master.

09:58.440 --> 09:59.390
Master.

09:59.440 --> 10:01.680
Maybe you should go check on Bai Shuo.

10:02.310 --> 10:04.330
She hasn't eaten or drunk anything for two days.

10:04.360 --> 10:06.220
She may die anytime.

10:06.370 --> 10:08.040
She knows what she wants.

10:08.820 --> 10:10.390
She won't let herself die.

10:10.410 --> 10:11.770
Then why is she so stubborn?

10:14.340 --> 10:16.340
It takes time to give in

10:16.430 --> 10:17.910
to someone you hate.

10:18.910 --> 10:20.320
I'm in no rush.

10:32.690 --> 10:34.690
Here's the best medicine

10:34.720 --> 10:36.520
and the sharpest knife in the Bright Moon Palace.

10:36.720 --> 10:37.930
Whether you live or die,

10:38.400 --> 10:39.240
it's your own choice.

10:43.330 --> 10:47.060
The Bright Moon Palace never feeds half-dead losers.

10:55.450 --> 10:56.560
You choose to die?

10:57.170 --> 10:58.320
I can help you.

10:58.930 --> 11:01.000
I'm the only one who can activate the Desireless Stone.

11:01.410 --> 11:02.710
You dare not kill me,

11:03.010 --> 11:04.300
nor can you.

11:04.600 --> 11:05.510
What?

11:06.280 --> 11:07.200
Are you really going to

11:07.200 --> 11:09.240
rely on a lifeless thing for the rest of your life?

11:09.590 --> 11:11.460
I thought you were a woman of character.

11:14.420 --> 11:16.430
If I were you, I would choose the medicine.

11:16.490 --> 11:19.170
After all, your pride is worthless now.

11:19.450 --> 11:21.120
If you can really hide in silence in front of your enemies

11:21.120 --> 11:23.630
and kill them with one strike,

11:24.390 --> 11:26.000
I might think better of you.

11:41.160 --> 11:42.460
I'll return it to you.

11:42.600 --> 11:43.790
I'll wait.

11:57.610 --> 11:58.970
Weren't you worried that she might choose the knife?

11:59.550 --> 12:01.150
She's not as weak as you think.

12:01.730 --> 12:03.160
Although she's a human,

12:03.180 --> 12:05.510
the fact that she dared to step into the Bright Moon Palace

12:05.610 --> 12:07.360
shows that she's braver than

12:07.360 --> 12:08.790
most people in the world.

12:09.510 --> 12:10.960
Why do I sense some

12:11.560 --> 12:13.280
admiration in your words?

12:19.520 --> 12:23.300
[Heart-guarding Cliff
Lanling Sect, Eternal Race]

12:29.090 --> 12:30.720
You want to detoxify,

12:30.750 --> 12:32.390
yet you refuse to report it to Lanling Sect.

12:33.070 --> 12:34.340
Why is that?

12:35.420 --> 12:36.840
Because you're scared.

12:37.450 --> 12:39.500
The human with the Desireless Stone in her body

12:39.530 --> 12:41.050
should be killed!

12:41.080 --> 12:43.160
If you're not capable enough, even if you use your sword,

12:43.430 --> 12:45.360
you'll only embarrass yourself.

12:45.390 --> 12:46.670
Logically,

12:46.720 --> 12:48.230
I have no right to blame you.

12:48.250 --> 12:49.610
But emotionally,

12:49.630 --> 12:51.510
I cannot help but blame you.

12:52.250 --> 12:53.920
From now on,

12:54.520 --> 12:55.880
we go

12:56.440 --> 12:57.480
our separate ways.

13:02.780 --> 13:05.260
Being distracted when practicing martial skills.

13:05.310 --> 13:07.160
Do you want to die, Divinity?

13:10.010 --> 13:11.480
It's you.

13:11.510 --> 13:13.020
I'll kill you!

13:17.140 --> 13:18.260
In Ning'an City,

13:18.290 --> 13:20.190
I saved you twice.

13:20.220 --> 13:21.500
Instead of thanking me,

13:21.520 --> 13:22.690
you want to kill me?

13:25.150 --> 13:27.610
I should have killed you in the clinic.

13:27.630 --> 13:28.980
Exactly. So

13:29.040 --> 13:30.640
why did you save me that night?

13:31.740 --> 13:33.170
You probably don't know that

13:33.200 --> 13:34.840
I killed the doctor in the clinic.

13:35.270 --> 13:36.700
I had no choice. He peeked at my body

13:36.720 --> 13:38.000
without permission.

13:38.020 --> 13:38.900
Tell me.

13:39.030 --> 13:40.460
Who do you think caused his death?

13:40.490 --> 13:42.210
You witch.

13:42.230 --> 13:44.030
You gave up a city for one person.

13:44.060 --> 13:45.020
Chong Zhao.

13:45.040 --> 13:46.590
How are you different from demons?

13:47.720 --> 13:49.720
The Eternal Race is truly cruel.

13:49.740 --> 13:51.260
You just made a tiny mistake,

13:51.290 --> 13:54.170
yet they erased your past achievements and exiled you here.

13:54.190 --> 13:56.500
The Heart-guarding Cliff is at the border of Lanling.

13:56.520 --> 13:57.920
If you take another step,

13:57.950 --> 13:59.970
you'll be out of the territory of the Eternal Race.

13:59.990 --> 14:01.230
Chong Zhao.

14:01.260 --> 14:02.650
Why don't you leave Lanling

14:02.670 --> 14:04.190
and join my Cold Spring Palace?

14:04.270 --> 14:05.360
Dream on!

14:05.360 --> 14:07.240
During Ning'an Xunyuan Lantern Festival,

14:07.270 --> 14:09.480
inexorable doom befell the Lanling Eternal Envoys.

14:09.570 --> 14:11.640
They never came back.

14:11.670 --> 14:14.000
Who is waiting for their return?

14:16.610 --> 14:18.410
How do you know these?

14:19.560 --> 14:20.610
I was bored

14:20.630 --> 14:22.200
and inquired about you.

14:22.230 --> 14:24.350
I found something strange.

14:24.390 --> 14:26.360
Ten years ago, during the Xunyuan Lantern Festival,

14:26.360 --> 14:28.710
the Human Race was attacked by the Demon Race, and hundreds of humans got killed or injured.

14:28.740 --> 14:30.340
The Eternal Envoy of Lanling, Chong Tai,

14:30.360 --> 14:32.200
and his wife, Meng Ning, were ordered to investigate,

14:32.230 --> 14:34.540
but they were killed by the scorpion demon, Qian Yin.

14:34.560 --> 14:35.930
His son, Chong Zhao,

14:35.960 --> 14:37.590
suspected the cause of death of his parents,

14:37.630 --> 14:39.060
yet he found nothing after years of investigation.

14:39.090 --> 14:40.640
What are you trying to say?

14:40.660 --> 14:42.110
The entire Eternal Race knows that your parents

14:42.140 --> 14:44.260
were killed by a scorpion demon ten years ago.

14:44.280 --> 14:45.470
But do you know that

14:45.510 --> 14:47.320
two days before your parents were killed,

14:47.340 --> 14:49.410
Qian Yin already died?

14:49.960 --> 14:52.560
You've been investigating for so many years, but you found nothing.

14:52.590 --> 14:53.790
Do you know why?

14:54.450 --> 14:55.450
Because

14:56.840 --> 14:59.050
you've never stepped on the territory of the Demon Race.

14:59.740 --> 15:00.620
Chong Zhao.

15:00.650 --> 15:02.290
What you see now

15:02.310 --> 15:03.950
may not be the truth.

15:03.980 --> 15:05.920
But somewhere you can't see,

15:06.000 --> 15:07.150
the truth

15:07.270 --> 15:08.910
might be right there.

15:12.870 --> 15:14.250
Clarify it!

15:14.520 --> 15:16.400
I'll wait for you in the Cold Spring Palace

15:16.420 --> 15:18.630
for a talk, Divinity Chong Zhao.

15:20.820 --> 15:21.730
Master.

15:21.760 --> 15:24.330
My parents were the best Eternal Envoys of Lanling.

15:24.350 --> 15:25.390
They killed countless demons.

15:25.420 --> 15:26.540
How could they have been

15:26.560 --> 15:28.470
killed by a scorpion demon?

15:28.510 --> 15:29.630
That's impossible!

15:29.630 --> 15:30.870
Kid.

15:30.890 --> 15:33.280
Didn't you see it with your own eyes?

15:34.010 --> 15:36.160
Your parents' soul lamps have gone out.

15:36.850 --> 15:38.170
It's all my fault.

15:38.310 --> 15:40.710
I underestimated the demonic power of Qian Yin

15:40.730 --> 15:42.730
and sent your parents to hunt him down,

15:42.760 --> 15:45.530
which ended up getting them killed.

15:45.560 --> 15:46.470
No!

15:46.490 --> 15:47.890
My father said

15:47.920 --> 15:49.280
that even if they encountered any danger,

15:48.340 --> 15:51.860
♫That year, that year♫

15:49.300 --> 15:52.060
one of them would come back alive.

15:52.090 --> 15:53.540
They wouldn't leave me behind.

15:52.490 --> 15:55.590
♫The leaves fell unnoticed after the flowers bloomed♫

15:53.560 --> 15:54.870
They said it.

15:56.380 --> 15:59.840
♫I'm afraid the autumn wind will stir up memories♫

15:59.390 --> 16:00.460
Don't worry.

16:00.620 --> 16:03.230
♫They unfold, one page after another♫

16:00.920 --> 16:03.440
I will kill Qian Yin myself

16:03.480 --> 16:05.150
and avenge your parents.

16:03.660 --> 16:07.310
♫That year, that year♫

16:05.150 --> 16:06.790
Cultivate well

16:06.790 --> 16:08.360
and live well.

16:07.520 --> 16:10.900
♫The flowers flew under the moon, filling the sky♫

16:09.000 --> 16:11.600
That'll be the best solace

16:11.400 --> 16:14.600
♫Falling to the mud, burying the memories♫

16:11.600 --> 16:13.440
to your parents' souls in heaven.

16:16.150 --> 16:18.570
♫Layer after layer♫

16:19.270 --> 16:22.180
♫Another year passed♫

16:27.120 --> 16:30.110
♫Another year passed♫

16:33.500 --> 16:35.700
I thought you were dead.

16:35.760 --> 16:37.280
Sorry to disappoint you.

16:37.300 --> 16:39.420
I would only be disappointed if you really died.

16:39.870 --> 16:41.560
Whether I have the Desireless Stone or not,

16:41.600 --> 16:43.150
I won't let myself die.

16:43.810 --> 16:44.990
Tell me then.

16:45.110 --> 16:46.270
What do you plan to do?

16:46.670 --> 16:47.720
I want to learn sorcery.

16:49.070 --> 16:50.350
Teach me yourself,

16:50.380 --> 16:51.860
or have someone else teach me.

16:53.200 --> 16:54.680
Why should I agree to that?

16:54.700 --> 16:56.890
Because I have the Desireless Stone in me.

16:56.920 --> 16:58.260
I may see the second image of foresight

16:58.320 --> 16:59.650
at any time.

16:59.750 --> 17:01.960
If you want to know where the next Contemplation will be born,

17:01.980 --> 17:03.170
you must agree to this.

17:04.480 --> 17:05.680
Are you threatening me?

17:06.069 --> 17:07.349
It's not a threat.

17:07.380 --> 17:08.490
As always,

17:08.510 --> 17:09.670
it's a deal.

17:11.510 --> 17:13.660
While the Desireless Stone is still inside you,

17:13.680 --> 17:15.920
you want to learn sorcery to protect yourself and strengthen your power.

17:17.220 --> 17:19.950
Only with bargaining chips can you do what you want.

17:21.359 --> 17:22.740
You have a clear mind

17:22.839 --> 17:24.319
and the right strategy.

17:24.339 --> 17:25.680
However,

17:25.730 --> 17:28.010
since you can make a deal out of the gathering of Contemplations,

17:28.380 --> 17:30.450
why don't you just ask me to avenge you?

17:31.100 --> 17:32.610
I must seek revenge in this world

17:32.870 --> 17:34.550
on my own.

17:36.150 --> 17:37.710
My father's suffering,

17:37.850 --> 17:39.000
the blood he shed,

17:39.430 --> 17:40.600
and the life he lost.

17:41.110 --> 17:41.880
One day,

17:41.880 --> 17:44.310
I will take it all back from them with my own hands.

17:45.200 --> 17:46.370
So, Master,

17:46.400 --> 17:47.580
will you teach me

17:47.600 --> 17:48.670
or not?

17:54.310 --> 17:56.030
Most of these weapons were

17:56.030 --> 17:57.690
left behind by the demons that were killed.

17:57.740 --> 17:59.940
So each weapon carries certain demonic power.

18:00.640 --> 18:02.000
Which weapon is the strongest?

18:04.160 --> 18:05.820
Greed won't do you any good.

18:05.850 --> 18:07.090
Since I want to practice,

18:07.110 --> 18:08.630
I'll practice with the most powerful weapon.

18:12.200 --> 18:13.680
This is a fire-wheel cane that was tempered

18:13.680 --> 18:15.640
by volcanoes for thousands of years.

18:15.670 --> 18:16.880
It weighs over 1,000 catties.

18:16.900 --> 18:18.410
The cane is covered with fire patterns.

18:18.440 --> 18:20.280
It's not something that ordinary people can lift up.

18:20.440 --> 18:21.830
They might even get hurt by the fire patterns

18:21.830 --> 18:23.440
and the demonic power within.

18:24.010 --> 18:25.160
Are you sure you want to practice with it?

18:26.170 --> 18:26.970
Yes.

18:55.100 --> 18:56.690
She actually lifted it up.

18:56.720 --> 18:58.140
Could it be that the Desireless Stone is helping her?

19:01.110 --> 19:03.590
I suggest you put it down now.

19:03.610 --> 19:04.820
I've said,

19:04.850 --> 19:06.720
I'll only practice with the most powerful weapon.

19:07.620 --> 19:09.400
♫May I ask, what do the gods see in the world?♫

19:09.650 --> 19:11.700
♫Sadness from infatuation, anger, and parting♫

19:11.930 --> 19:13.150
If you don't put it down now,

19:12.160 --> 19:13.540
♫My love brought tears♫

19:13.180 --> 19:14.620
your hands will be crippled.

19:13.970 --> 19:15.720
♫Greed for gathering, for holding, and for completeness♫

19:15.970 --> 19:17.740
♫I was never a flower, but I withered on my own♫

19:17.970 --> 19:19.080
♫I fell between your brows and became a good fruit♫

19:19.570 --> 19:21.580
♫The grand dream of life is hard to let go♫

19:21.790 --> 19:23.400
♫Searching for the path, the answers, yet found nothing♫

19:23.860 --> 19:25.430
♫With a heart full of compassion for the people, I let go of my obsessions♫

19:25.770 --> 19:27.670
♫I cultivated myself to be free of desires, offering myself as a sacrifice to the moon♫

19:27.790 --> 19:29.710
♫The daylight burns through, and the stars shine bright♫

19:30.310 --> 19:31.900
♫Through the Buddhist dust, I see the moon in the sky♫

19:32.090 --> 19:33.830
♫I am but a mortal, destined to fade♫

19:34.100 --> 19:36.120
♫But I went through a thousand calamities for a promise♫

19:36.330 --> 19:37.860
♫I severed emotions, desires, and the fate between you and me♫

19:38.230 --> 19:40.770
Please bless the world♫To protect the world for eternity♫

19:41.290 --> 19:42.400
Tian Huo.

19:42.420 --> 19:43.500
Escort her back.

19:43.530 --> 19:45.100
I haven't said I couldn't do it.

19:51.940 --> 19:53.260
I said,

19:53.280 --> 19:54.150
go back.

19:54.940 --> 19:56.660
I never said I couldn't do it.

19:56.680 --> 19:58.200
Are you moved by yourself?

19:58.780 --> 20:00.020
In my eyes,

20:00.180 --> 20:01.420
you're just foolish.

20:02.040 --> 20:03.630
I just don't want to give up.

20:04.130 --> 20:05.470
My injuries will heal,

20:05.630 --> 20:06.950
but the training can't stop.

20:07.850 --> 20:09.050
It takes a lot more than bravery

20:09.070 --> 20:10.360
to achieve great things.

20:10.670 --> 20:12.040
If you get your hands crippled,

20:12.060 --> 20:13.620
I won't teach you anymore.

20:15.120 --> 20:16.080
Tian Huo.

20:16.680 --> 20:17.630
Escort her back.

20:27.640 --> 20:29.130
You're cold and distant,

20:29.150 --> 20:31.180
and your dressing skills are average.

20:32.060 --> 20:33.420
I don't think our relationship is so close

20:33.590 --> 20:35.660
that we can talk about this.

20:36.210 --> 20:37.610
Let me remind you again.

20:37.900 --> 20:40.620
Outside the Bright Moon Palace is the Polar Region that stretches for hundreds of thousands of miles.

20:40.650 --> 20:41.830
There are demons and monsters everywhere.

20:41.850 --> 20:43.400
Don't wander around.

20:43.430 --> 20:44.840
I won't be responsible if you lose your life.

20:45.400 --> 20:46.600
I don't need your reminder.

20:47.230 --> 20:49.680
I have more important things to do with my life.

20:49.840 --> 20:51.160
That would be the best.

20:51.420 --> 20:52.870
Don't make Master worry about you.

20:53.560 --> 20:54.800
You care about Fan Yue a lot?

20:56.480 --> 20:58.250
Everyone in the Bright Moon Palace

20:58.270 --> 20:59.980
cares a lot about Master.

21:00.070 --> 21:01.510
So just stay here and be good.

21:01.680 --> 21:03.900
Master will teach you when he wants to.

21:04.010 --> 21:06.640
Don't have any ulterior thoughts.

21:07.510 --> 21:09.080
Ulterior thoughts?

21:10.180 --> 21:11.860
Does the thought of killing him count?

21:12.030 --> 21:13.750
Before you kill him,

21:13.880 --> 21:15.520
I'll kill you.

21:15.740 --> 21:17.500
Even if I have to die with you.

21:19.370 --> 21:20.470
I see.

21:20.520 --> 21:21.480
Please see yourself out.

21:29.510 --> 21:31.990
I haven't achieved anything, yet my hands are already injured.

21:32.360 --> 21:33.720
Brute force alone

21:33.780 --> 21:35.330
is indeed useless.

21:39.170 --> 21:45.570
♫Love is the hardest thing to understand♫

21:43.110 --> 21:44.260
I'm done practicing.

21:45.090 --> 21:46.530
You were the one who said you wanted to learn,

21:46.130 --> 21:53.140
♫I'm finally back to where it all started♫

21:46.550 --> 21:48.550
and now you are the one who wants to give up.

21:48.630 --> 21:50.230
How can my daughter be such a loser?

21:50.640 --> 21:52.240
Can I learn it well if I don't give up?

21:53.670 --> 21:59.350
♫All the answers are already explained♫

22:01.400 --> 22:03.780
♫I'll owe you all of my life♫

22:03.060 --> 22:03.970
Shuo.

22:04.560 --> 22:07.610
♫But we're destined to part♫

22:05.580 --> 22:07.390
You may not succeed if you don't give up.

22:08.330 --> 22:10.050
But if you give up, you'll definitely fail.

22:08.460 --> 22:14.450
♫How can I downplay this?♫

22:11.710 --> 22:12.750
I believe in you.

22:15.060 --> 22:18.290
♫When you engrave your love into my heart♫

22:18.980 --> 22:21.860
♫When my star falls only for you♫

22:19.980 --> 22:21.390
Father.

22:21.910 --> 22:23.180
Sorry.

22:22.810 --> 22:24.060
♫When the heavens fall♫

22:23.830 --> 22:25.620
I've chosen to work with demons.

22:24.710 --> 22:29.760
♫I can still connect with you through the waning moon♫

22:26.630 --> 22:29.120
I'm not sure where I'm headed yet.

22:29.140 --> 22:31.060
But no matter what kind of path it is,

22:30.090 --> 22:32.980
♫When my pain blurs my eyes♫

22:31.090 --> 22:33.440
I will step on it,

22:33.460 --> 22:34.950
take the revenge

22:33.570 --> 22:37.630
♫Out of the countless stars, I see only you♫

22:34.970 --> 22:36.610
and repay the kindness that is due

22:36.640 --> 22:38.110
step by step.

22:38.270 --> 22:42.650
♫As you turn into a falling star♫

22:38.930 --> 22:39.960
Don't worry.

22:40.450 --> 22:42.880
I will forge my own path.

22:52.960 --> 22:53.940
Get out of my way.

22:54.210 --> 22:55.280
Where is Fan Yue?

22:55.310 --> 22:56.680
Do you think Master's whereabouts

22:56.680 --> 22:57.980
is something you can inquire about casually?

22:58.020 --> 22:59.310
He promised to teach me sorcery,

22:59.330 --> 23:00.720
but I haven't seen him for days.

23:00.750 --> 23:02.030
Did he regret it?

23:02.070 --> 23:03.240
Since Master said he would teach you,

23:03.260 --> 23:04.510
of course he won't break his promise.

23:04.540 --> 23:05.820
But he also said

23:05.900 --> 23:07.300
if your hands were crippled,

23:07.330 --> 23:08.640
he wouldn't teach you anymore.

23:08.680 --> 23:10.120
My hands have recovered.

23:10.160 --> 23:11.810
Then wait for him to come and teach you.

23:11.840 --> 23:13.420
He will come when he wants to.

23:13.900 --> 23:16.340
It's supposed to be a deal, and we should be equal.

23:16.370 --> 23:18.090
Why is the Bright Moon Palace so overbearing?

23:18.110 --> 23:19.910
It can't be helped. You are in the Bright Moon Palace now,

23:19.940 --> 23:22.140
so the final say is Master's.

23:23.400 --> 23:25.650
You're obviously abusing your power and bullying me.

23:25.680 --> 23:26.890
In the Demon Race,

23:26.910 --> 23:27.630
power is gained through

23:27.680 --> 23:28.750
countless fights

23:28.750 --> 23:30.350
with fists or swords.

23:30.380 --> 23:31.730
Don't you think

23:31.750 --> 23:32.640
it's reasonable for us to use our power to bully others?

23:33.530 --> 23:34.570
What kind of logic is that?

23:34.660 --> 23:36.070
That's the logic of the Demon Race.

23:36.390 --> 23:37.390
If you are unhappy about it,

23:37.440 --> 23:39.010
either become stronger yourself,

23:39.040 --> 23:40.600
or go back to your Human Race.

23:49.850 --> 23:51.680
Since you have the intention to teach her, Master,

23:51.710 --> 23:53.320
why have you been ignoring her for so many days?

23:54.090 --> 23:55.570
She's too eager for success.

23:55.850 --> 23:58.010
No matter what she practices, it will be counterproductive.

23:58.830 --> 24:00.790
So you're doing this for her own good, Master?

24:00.820 --> 24:02.280
For her good?

24:02.590 --> 24:03.920
I just don't want

24:03.920 --> 24:06.110
a useless ally with crippled hands and feet.

24:07.110 --> 24:08.790
You think she is useless, Master,

24:09.300 --> 24:11.190
yet you still treat her as your ally.

24:22.210 --> 24:23.650
So untrustworthy.

24:23.680 --> 24:25.000
Breaking his promise.

24:25.030 --> 24:26.460
If he didn't want to teach me, why didn't he just refuse?

24:27.270 --> 24:28.310
If it goes on like this,

24:28.310 --> 24:30.000
when will I ever become stronger?

24:30.610 --> 24:31.370
This won't do.

24:31.850 --> 24:33.790
I can't wait like this any longer.

24:33.820 --> 24:35.570
I'll go ask Fan Yue to explain this to me.

24:43.420 --> 24:45.660
Where is he going at such a late hour?

25:11.170 --> 25:12.850
What is this place?

25:12.870 --> 25:14.240
So secretive.

25:14.330 --> 25:16.740
Could this be a secret place for cultivation?

25:16.760 --> 25:17.870
Or,

25:17.990 --> 25:19.400
maybe it's a treasure trove?

25:44.890 --> 25:46.290
What are these?

25:47.010 --> 25:48.170
Ju Ying.

25:48.210 --> 25:49.410
You Nan.

25:49.440 --> 25:50.760
Qi Feng?

25:51.090 --> 25:52.840
They all seem to be names.

25:53.310 --> 25:54.550
Why are they hung here?

25:55.230 --> 25:56.770
They look quite old.

25:56.890 --> 25:58.770
Are these antiques collected by Fan Yue?

26:05.830 --> 26:06.880
Fan Yue?

26:07.290 --> 26:08.860
Why is his name also on it?

26:09.450 --> 26:10.210
Come out!

26:17.560 --> 26:18.750
How did you get in here?

26:18.830 --> 26:20.110
How did I get in?

26:20.140 --> 26:21.590
I followed you in.

26:22.480 --> 26:23.110
Get out.

26:24.270 --> 26:25.330
Fan Yue.

26:25.360 --> 26:27.800
You've ignored me for so many days. That should be enough, right?

26:27.820 --> 26:30.050
Or are you teasing me on purpose?

26:30.080 --> 26:31.560
You promised to teach me,

26:31.590 --> 26:33.460
but you've been nowhere to be found all day.

26:33.500 --> 26:35.200
I didn't expect to see you

26:35.200 --> 26:37.140
admiring your antiques here.

26:37.170 --> 26:38.550
What's so precious about these that you need to collect them?

26:41.160 --> 26:43.200
I allowed you to stay here and walk freely in the Bright Moon Palace.

26:43.240 --> 26:44.680
That doesn't mean you can break into my secret chamber

26:44.680 --> 26:45.960
and pry into my secrets!

26:45.980 --> 26:47.550
Those who talk too much should be killed,

26:47.580 --> 26:48.970
those who are reckless deserve to die,

26:48.990 --> 26:50.740
and those who are overly curious have no right to live!

26:50.760 --> 26:52.720
Don't try to challenge my tolerance.

26:52.750 --> 26:54.070
If this happens again,

26:54.090 --> 26:55.240
even if I have to give up the Desireless Stone,

26:55.240 --> 26:56.860
I will destroy you.

26:56.880 --> 26:58.430
What about that thing you promised me?

26:58.960 --> 27:01.480
You're only using the Demon Race's logic to bully me

27:01.500 --> 27:03.070
because you are strong.

27:03.100 --> 27:04.580
So what's wrong with me wanting to become stronger?

27:04.600 --> 27:06.890
I used to understand the feeling of wanting to become stronger even better than you.

27:06.930 --> 27:07.680
You're not the only one

27:07.680 --> 27:09.270
who has experienced tremendous changes, Bai Shuo!

27:09.560 --> 27:11.190
Don't think you're so special.

27:11.220 --> 27:13.490
If you want to become stronger, you have to endure the process of it.

27:13.510 --> 27:14.920
You want to accomplish it at one stroke?

27:14.950 --> 27:15.830
Dream on!

27:16.100 --> 27:16.820
Get lost!

27:50.650 --> 27:52.810
[Gu Shang
Chief of Baize Clan, Demon Race]

27:51.180 --> 27:52.020
Yue.

27:52.040 --> 27:52.970
You're awake?

27:53.820 --> 27:54.970
You're awake.

27:55.000 --> 27:56.110
You're awake.

27:56.160 --> 27:56.880
Yue.

27:56.410 --> 27:58.010
[Young Fan Yue
Baize Clan, Demon Race]

27:56.910 --> 27:58.150
Who are you?

27:59.070 --> 28:01.200
Yue. I'm Grandfather.

28:02.680 --> 28:04.110
Grandfather?

28:05.750 --> 28:06.920
Yue.

28:06.940 --> 28:08.970
How come you don't even remember Grandfather?

28:09.000 --> 28:09.850
What about me?

28:09.880 --> 28:11.410
Do you remember me?

28:11.440 --> 28:12.480
You are...

28:12.910 --> 28:15.150
[Young Qi Feng
Baize Clan, Demon Race]

28:13.200 --> 28:14.310
I'm Qi Feng,

28:14.310 --> 28:15.310
your younger brother.

28:15.960 --> 28:18.040
Is your brain damaged

28:18.070 --> 28:19.550
from that fall from the mountain?

28:19.570 --> 28:20.480
Qi Feng.

28:21.170 --> 28:22.730
There's no need to be afraid.

28:22.760 --> 28:23.960
If you can't remember,

28:23.980 --> 28:25.730
stop thinking about it.

28:25.760 --> 28:27.280
Since you're seriously injured,

28:27.300 --> 28:29.400
the most important thing for now is to recover.

28:29.450 --> 28:30.730
This is your home.

28:30.760 --> 28:31.760
Just

28:31.830 --> 28:32.790
stay here with peace of mind.

28:33.530 --> 28:34.530
So I...

28:35.160 --> 28:36.310
I am...

28:36.740 --> 28:38.170
Fan Yue.

28:38.510 --> 28:40.220
That's your name.

28:41.440 --> 28:43.160
Fan Yue...

28:43.390 --> 28:46.730
♫The person standing far away♫

28:47.740 --> 28:49.520
♫Don't be afraid♫

28:50.450 --> 28:54.820
♫The stars will guide you to me♫

28:56.010 --> 29:02.400
♫Walk towards me♫

28:56.480 --> 28:58.000
Have some of this.

28:58.000 --> 28:58.440
Here.

28:58.440 --> 28:59.720
Chief.

29:02.050 --> 29:03.890
Yue, here.

29:03.920 --> 29:06.320
Grandfather said that once a member of the Baize Clan turns 15,

29:04.330 --> 29:06.910
♫My heart feels so...♫

29:06.370 --> 29:08.130
he or she can drink the holy spring water of our clan.

29:07.520 --> 29:13.340
♫It's pounding as I wait for you♫

29:08.160 --> 29:09.110
We're just the right age.

29:09.680 --> 29:10.270
Here.

29:10.270 --> 29:11.510
Try it too.

29:11.510 --> 29:12.350
Try it.

29:15.340 --> 29:19.000
♫The stars light up your eyes♫

29:21.160 --> 29:22.680
It's indeed hard to get used to it the first time you drink it.

29:22.680 --> 29:24.000
Drink it a few more times, and it'll get better.

29:22.840 --> 29:25.990
♫You are my distant call♫

29:24.000 --> 29:25.030
-Let's drink.
-Cheers.

29:25.030 --> 29:26.240
Chief.

29:26.240 --> 29:27.240
Chief.

29:26.670 --> 29:30.600
♫You are my first and last♫

29:27.240 --> 29:28.480
Please put the nameplate on our daughter

29:28.480 --> 29:29.590
and give her your blessings.

29:29.870 --> 29:31.250
She's really grown up.

29:31.720 --> 29:32.590
Here.

29:31.870 --> 29:37.780
♫My heart is trembling for you♫

29:33.030 --> 29:34.240
Let me put

29:34.240 --> 29:35.790
this nameplate on our

29:35.790 --> 29:37.590
beautiful new member of Baize Clan.

29:35.990 --> 29:37.880
[Yun Nuan]

29:37.590 --> 29:39.240
Thank you, Grandfather.

29:38.380 --> 29:41.000
♫In this moment where we embrace each other♫

29:39.240 --> 29:40.790
You're welcome.

29:42.030 --> 29:46.740
♫Let's never let go♫

29:44.030 --> 29:45.020
Yue.

29:45.060 --> 29:47.190
This is a tradition of our clan.

29:47.240 --> 29:48.970
We forge

29:49.110 --> 29:50.430
a nameplate for each new member

29:50.480 --> 29:52.270
of Baize Clan.

29:52.350 --> 29:54.000
You had one too.

29:54.540 --> 29:57.300
But when you fell down from the mountain,

29:57.400 --> 29:59.670
the nameplate blocked some damage for you,

29:59.700 --> 30:01.750
and it was broken by a stone.

30:01.800 --> 30:03.080
I've asked someone

30:03.110 --> 30:05.260
to forge a new one for you.

30:05.280 --> 30:06.440
In the future,

30:05.700 --> 30:09.500
♫We're destined to be together forever from the first sight♫

30:06.470 --> 30:07.550
our dear Yue

30:07.590 --> 30:08.440
will definitely be

30:08.440 --> 30:09.880
safe

30:09.880 --> 30:11.920
and healthy.

30:10.680 --> 30:12.480
♫Goodbye, loneliness♫

30:13.670 --> 30:16.560
♫The one who was slightly late♫

30:14.320 --> 30:14.880
Yue.

30:14.900 --> 30:16.340
Let's go dance.

30:16.370 --> 30:17.240
Dance?

30:17.280 --> 30:17.970
Want to go together?

30:18.000 --> 30:20.590
I'll go too. I'll go too.

30:18.040 --> 30:24.770
♫You came towards me, closer and closer♫

30:26.430 --> 30:33.280
♫You enriched my life♫

30:33.810 --> 30:37.260
♫The stars light up your eyes♫

30:41.190 --> 30:44.970
♫You are the light I yearn for♫

30:45.590 --> 30:48.390
♫You are my determined way home♫

31:11.680 --> 31:13.270
What's wrong with me wanting to become stronger?

31:13.270 --> 31:15.480
I used to understand the feeling of wanting to become stronger even better than you.

31:15.480 --> 31:16.270
You're not the only one

31:16.270 --> 31:17.920
who has experienced tremendous changes, Bai Shuo!

31:17.920 --> 31:19.390
Don't think you're so special.

31:19.420 --> 31:22.110
If you want to become stronger, you have to endure the process of it.

31:22.130 --> 31:23.090
Get lost!

31:26.170 --> 31:28.170
Could it be that he experienced some unspeakable pain

31:28.200 --> 31:30.140
in his past?

31:30.860 --> 31:32.790
What are those nameplates?

31:33.020 --> 31:34.700
They seem to be very important to Fan Yue.

31:35.360 --> 31:37.640
Are they meant to commemorate something?

31:42.960 --> 31:44.750
Lady Fu Ling. You've been working till so late.

31:44.750 --> 31:46.790
Are you trying to please Grand Master,

31:46.790 --> 31:48.550
or are you worried Grand Master will punish you?

31:51.050 --> 31:52.200
What are you trying to say?

31:52.230 --> 31:54.320
Grand Master asked you to drag Chong Zhao into the Demon Race,

31:54.340 --> 31:55.730
and he gave you a month.

31:55.760 --> 31:57.390
It's been half a month.

31:57.410 --> 31:58.780
You still haven't completed this task?

31:59.590 --> 32:01.460
Everything is under my control.

32:01.490 --> 32:02.970
Don't you worry about it.

32:03.620 --> 32:04.750
If you have so much free time,

32:04.780 --> 32:06.140
maybe you should think about

32:06.160 --> 32:08.080
how to walk out of the Cold Spring Palace standing.

32:26.180 --> 32:28.350
He tried to kill me yesterday,

32:28.370 --> 32:29.850
yet I've come to admit defeat to him today.

32:29.880 --> 32:31.270
It does seem too cowardly.

32:32.510 --> 32:33.550
But

32:33.570 --> 32:34.920
enduring bitterness

32:34.950 --> 32:36.510
is a must on my way to become stronger.

32:36.530 --> 32:37.900
There's nothing I can't overcome.

32:39.270 --> 32:40.270
What's up?

32:40.570 --> 32:41.410
I'm here to bring you food.

32:49.660 --> 32:51.350
What kind of new trick is this?

32:51.380 --> 32:53.940
I followed you into the secret chamber yesterday on purpose,

32:53.960 --> 32:55.850
and the purpose was to get something on you

32:55.880 --> 32:57.200
so that I could force you to teach me sorcery.

32:57.720 --> 32:58.810
You suddenly came clean to me?

32:59.340 --> 33:00.540
I couldn't hide it from you in the first place,

33:00.570 --> 33:01.770
so I might as well tell you frankly.

33:01.790 --> 33:03.460
I don't know what those nameplates

33:03.490 --> 33:04.620
in the forbidden chamber mean to you,

33:05.090 --> 33:07.350
but I did pry into your privacy.

33:07.780 --> 33:08.650
I apologize.

33:09.750 --> 33:12.660
You can really yield in order to become stronger.

33:12.690 --> 33:13.930
So, Master,

33:13.950 --> 33:15.400
are you willing to teach me this time?

33:15.430 --> 33:16.720
Go back first.

33:16.820 --> 33:18.060
I'll think about it.

33:19.480 --> 33:21.690
I hope it won't take you too long, Master.

33:29.160 --> 33:30.280
Stop pretending.

33:30.410 --> 33:32.020
I don't buy it.

33:36.190 --> 33:36.800
Bai Shuo.

33:55.440 --> 33:56.270
Tell me.

33:56.270 --> 33:57.110
What did you do?

33:58.480 --> 34:00.110
What do you think I could do?

34:03.990 --> 34:05.190
What is this?

34:05.210 --> 34:06.780
This is the trace left by demonic power's devoration.

34:07.500 --> 34:08.800
Tell me the truth already.

34:08.830 --> 34:09.949
What on earth did you do?

34:10.590 --> 34:12.360
What do you think I could do?

34:13.280 --> 34:14.670
I just practiced

34:30.710 --> 34:32.480
the mental cultivation methods of the Demon Race secretly.

34:32.510 --> 34:34.110
You're really something, Bai Shuo.

34:34.130 --> 34:36.300
I was just too impatient.

34:37.290 --> 34:39.010
So what happened to me?

34:39.100 --> 34:40.650
You can't cultivate demonic power.

34:40.929 --> 34:42.050
Why?

34:42.080 --> 34:43.940
Maybe it's because of the Desireless Stone.

34:44.010 --> 34:45.969
Isn't the Desireless Stone a divine object?

34:46.000 --> 34:47.730
Could it prevent people from becoming stronger?

34:47.750 --> 34:48.590
Maybe it's exactly because

34:48.590 --> 34:50.889
the Desireless Stone is a divine object that it caused this.

34:51.000 --> 34:52.440
What do you mean?

34:52.469 --> 34:55.239
The current mental cultivation methods of the Demon Race are passed down from the ancient Demon Race,

34:55.520 --> 34:57.920
while the mental cultivation methods of the Eternal Race are passed down from the ancient Lunar Race.

34:57.940 --> 34:59.460
The Desireless Stone is the sacred object of the Lunar Race.

34:59.490 --> 35:01.010
It's against the Demon Race's methods.

35:01.450 --> 35:02.740
That's why

35:02.770 --> 35:04.520
the more you cultivate the mental methods of the Demon Race,

35:04.540 --> 35:06.540
the more serious the devoration you'll suffer.

35:06.570 --> 35:08.980
I only heard there are gods and demons in this world.

35:09.480 --> 35:11.190
What are the ancient

35:11.220 --> 35:12.600
Lunar Race

35:12.660 --> 35:13.660
and Demon Race?

35:13.840 --> 35:16.120
Sixty thousand years ago, there was the ancient Divine Race,

35:16.140 --> 35:18.260
which was divided into three sections, namely Lunar, Demon, and Hidden.

35:18.290 --> 35:20.620
Later, Hidden Lord, Mo Li, caused a catastrophe to the world.

35:20.650 --> 35:23.250
In the end, he was killed by Lunar Lord, Xing Yue, and Demon Lord, Jing Yuan.

35:23.270 --> 35:25.940
But in this Divine War, the Divine Region was destroyed,

35:25.970 --> 35:27.410
and all deities fell.

35:27.430 --> 35:29.070
From then on, there were no more deities in the world.

35:30.690 --> 35:32.100
You mean

35:32.630 --> 35:34.550
if I want to become stronger,

35:34.590 --> 35:36.230
I can only practice the methods of the Eternal Race?

35:36.530 --> 35:38.220
Why do I sense betrayal

35:38.250 --> 35:39.930
in your eyes?

35:40.630 --> 35:42.110
You're overthinking it.

35:42.140 --> 35:43.620
Even if I defect to the Eternal Race,

35:43.670 --> 35:45.890
those old men of the Eternal Race won't avenge me.

35:45.910 --> 35:47.620
They'll control me instead.

35:48.230 --> 35:50.190
And you won't let me off the hook, either.

35:50.290 --> 35:51.480
If I join the Eternal Race,

35:51.500 --> 35:52.830
it won't be worth it.

35:52.860 --> 35:54.090
You're quite wise.

35:55.480 --> 35:56.560
Get up.

35:56.590 --> 35:57.720
I'll take you to a place.

35:58.930 --> 36:00.000
Where?

36:00.070 --> 36:01.510
Lanling Sect.

36:01.540 --> 36:03.190
What's that supposed to mean?

36:03.300 --> 36:05.420
Are you colluding with your enemy as Master of the Bright Moon Palace?

36:05.450 --> 36:07.040
Didn't you say that

36:07.070 --> 36:08.370
either I teach you

36:08.400 --> 36:10.150
or I find someone to teach you?

36:11.080 --> 36:12.330
Who're you going to ask to teach me?

36:12.360 --> 36:13.440
You'll know when you get there.

36:43.110 --> 36:45.040
[Old Turtle
1000-year-old Mystery Turtle, Eternal Race]

36:45.590 --> 36:47.430
This is the territory of Lanling.

36:47.450 --> 36:49.130
Why can you go in and out freely?

36:49.160 --> 36:50.350
I have my own way.

36:50.380 --> 36:51.900
The master you got for me

36:51.920 --> 36:54.080
is not an Eternal of Lanling, is he?

36:54.110 --> 36:55.630
Eternals and demons have always been enemies.

36:55.650 --> 36:57.010
Why are you so close?

36:57.040 --> 36:58.270
The rules are fixed,

36:58.290 --> 36:59.560
but those who enforce them can be flexible.

36:59.590 --> 37:00.840
That's not wrong.

37:03.580 --> 37:04.550
Why aren't we going in?

37:05.030 --> 37:06.030
He already ran away.

37:08.000 --> 37:09.000
Where are we going?

37:09.030 --> 37:09.880
To catch the tortoise.

37:14.870 --> 37:16.990
Put me down!

37:22.510 --> 37:24.110
Stop it!

37:24.110 --> 37:26.710
If you keep pulling the thread, my shell will crack.

37:26.710 --> 37:28.610
Is this the Eternal you talked about?

37:28.650 --> 37:29.770
A real tor...

37:31.050 --> 37:32.200
Turtle.

37:32.470 --> 37:33.990
He's the 1000-year-old Mystery Turtle.

37:34.010 --> 37:34.970
He's lived longer

37:35.000 --> 37:36.850
than the Five Eternals of Lanling.

37:38.760 --> 37:41.320
Given his species, he can't die young even if he wants to.

37:51.950 --> 37:53.140
My old...

37:57.190 --> 37:59.250
I once saved your life in the Eternal Race.

37:59.280 --> 38:00.200
Now,

38:00.220 --> 38:01.410
I'm here to collect the debt.

38:09.780 --> 38:10.700
Fan Yue.

38:12.550 --> 38:14.960
Why did you come to the Eternal Race's territory

38:15.140 --> 38:16.620
instead of staying in the Polar Region?

38:19.510 --> 38:21.280
Demon King of the Polar Region.

38:21.280 --> 38:23.320
Master of the Bright Moon Palace.

38:23.320 --> 38:25.400
Here comes another demon king.

38:27.440 --> 38:28.490
Zhen Yu.

38:28.700 --> 38:30.780
I feel like you're actually regressing.

38:31.360 --> 38:32.910
As the Demon King,

38:32.930 --> 38:34.410
you actually chased after a turtle?

38:34.440 --> 38:36.440
I'm the 1000-year-old Mystery Turtle.

38:39.360 --> 38:40.320
The one in Lanling?

38:41.630 --> 38:42.670
He knows me!

38:43.440 --> 38:44.070
He...

38:44.070 --> 38:46.520
I can do whatever I want.

38:46.600 --> 38:47.400
What?

38:47.420 --> 38:48.460
Today,

38:48.490 --> 38:49.820
you want to get involved

38:50.010 --> 38:51.300
and help the Eternal Race?

38:52.560 --> 38:53.690
So what if I help them?

38:54.380 --> 38:56.090
The Jingyou Mountain has been silent for years.

38:56.120 --> 38:58.180
Word has it in the Demon Race that the Three Kings have been fighting.

38:58.550 --> 38:59.510
But it seems to me that

38:59.510 --> 39:01.280
it's just a fight between you and me.

39:02.000 --> 39:03.250
I will save

39:03.280 --> 39:04.640
whoever you want to kill.

39:04.730 --> 39:06.220
And I'll oppose

39:06.290 --> 39:07.610
whatever you want to do.

39:10.000 --> 39:11.230
Haughty.

39:12.170 --> 39:13.170
Good.

39:13.210 --> 39:14.850
Let me see

39:15.410 --> 39:17.450
whether you, the new king of the Demon Race,

39:17.480 --> 39:19.060
deserve

39:19.230 --> 39:21.000
your arrogance.

39:43.480 --> 39:44.440
Zhen Yu.

39:45.000 --> 39:45.880
You are too old.

39:46.580 --> 39:47.580
If you ask me,

39:48.170 --> 39:49.170
there doesn't have to be Three Kings

39:49.580 --> 39:50.850
in the Demon Race.

39:51.880 --> 39:54.590
Fan Yue, don't get cocky too soon.

39:54.620 --> 39:55.980
One day,

39:56.030 --> 39:59.030
I'll avenge the loss of my tail.

40:03.440 --> 40:05.800
The teleportation formation I gave you back then

40:05.800 --> 40:08.840
was for you to come to Lanling to see me anytime.

40:08.840 --> 40:10.070
But look at you.

40:10.070 --> 40:12.070
You haven't come to see me even once over these years.

40:12.070 --> 40:14.880
You even stole the Desireless Stone with the treasure I gave you.

40:14.880 --> 40:17.150
Public morals are indeed degenerating with each passing day.

40:18.360 --> 40:19.840
Demons are heartless.

40:19.840 --> 40:21.370
Why do I remember

40:21.390 --> 40:23.710
we made the plan to steal the Desireless Stone together?

40:23.740 --> 40:25.260
Don't talk nonsense!

40:25.280 --> 40:26.590
It has nothing to do with me.

40:26.620 --> 40:28.230
You stole it yourself.

40:28.400 --> 40:29.960
But Jin Yao must be very curious

40:29.960 --> 40:32.280
how I broke through all the barriers of the Eternals

40:32.280 --> 40:34.370
and walked so freely in Lanling, don't you think?

40:34.510 --> 40:36.840
What exactly do you want?

40:36.840 --> 40:38.090
Use your elixir

40:38.110 --> 40:39.240
to cure her devoration.

40:40.030 --> 40:40.880
What devoration?

40:42.880 --> 40:45.070
The devoration caused by the conflict between the Desireless Stone and the demonic power.

40:46.150 --> 40:46.710
You...

40:47.360 --> 40:49.550
So you're the human who absorbed the Desireless Stone?

40:49.550 --> 40:50.440
You...

40:50.440 --> 40:51.360
Are you going to treat her or not?

40:52.880 --> 40:54.590
Sure. Sure I will.

40:54.590 --> 40:55.230
Also,

40:56.110 --> 40:57.190
teach her the Eternals' sorcery.

41:00.980 --> 41:02.870
You may as well tell Jin Yao

41:02.900 --> 41:04.780
that I let you in.

41:04.800 --> 41:06.720
I'll only lose a layer of my shell for colluding with the enemy.

41:06.750 --> 41:09.430
But if I teach her, I'm afraid I won't live to be a 1000-year-old tortoise.

41:09.480 --> 41:10.630
I wouldn't dare to offend those five Eternals

41:10.630 --> 41:12.450
at the same time.

41:12.740 --> 41:14.190
Aren't you the 1000-year-old Mystery Turtle

41:14.190 --> 41:15.670
born from the spiritual energy of heaven and earth?

41:15.670 --> 41:17.350
Why should you be scared of the Five Eternals?

41:18.480 --> 41:19.630
The Five Eternals are not scary.

41:19.630 --> 41:20.840
What's scary is the Desireless Stone.

41:20.840 --> 41:22.320
You have the Desireless Stone in you,

41:22.320 --> 41:24.590
so all the Eternals and demons in the world want you.

41:24.620 --> 41:26.030
Even if I'm a 1000-year-old tortoise,

41:26.030 --> 41:27.510
I wouldn't be able to handle it.

41:27.510 --> 41:28.320
Alright.

41:28.320 --> 41:29.280
Cut the crap.

41:29.620 --> 41:30.340
Either

41:30.370 --> 41:31.330
teach her,

41:31.350 --> 41:32.380
or

41:32.410 --> 41:33.860
give your life back to me now.

41:34.420 --> 41:36.020
Calm down. Calm down.

41:36.320 --> 41:37.440
I'll teach her.

41:41.070 --> 41:42.550
Are you sure you want this turtle who knows no bounds

41:42.550 --> 41:44.670
to be my master?

41:44.670 --> 41:46.360
What do you think he can teach me?

41:52.760 --> 41:53.880
Eat this.

41:53.880 --> 41:55.840
Your devoration will subside soon.

41:57.710 --> 41:58.790
Is it that powerful?

41:58.810 --> 42:00.040
Of course.

42:00.070 --> 42:03.800
If I rank second in healing,

42:03.820 --> 42:07.120
no one dares to call themselves number one.

42:07.640 --> 42:10.450
That's exactly what the quack who sold me fake medicine many years ago said.

42:10.480 --> 42:13.110
How dare you compare me to those quacks?

42:13.110 --> 42:14.880
Take it, or give it back to me.

42:14.880 --> 42:16.400
I was just saying.

42:16.400 --> 42:17.320
It's just I encountered too many swindlers

42:17.320 --> 42:18.670
in the past.

42:18.800 --> 42:19.800
Of course I trust

42:19.800 --> 42:20.920
the person Master introduced to me.

42:44.710 --> 42:45.480
How is it?

42:45.480 --> 42:46.400
Is the demonic pattern gone?

42:47.100 --> 42:48.310
Look.

42:48.330 --> 42:49.350
Look.

42:50.320 --> 42:51.480
Old Turtle, look.

42:51.480 --> 42:52.670
It's gone. It's gone.

42:52.670 --> 42:54.590
You're a girl. Watch your behavior.

42:55.360 --> 42:56.760
What's wrong with my behavior?

42:57.850 --> 42:58.920
Catch it.

43:00.150 --> 43:01.070
What is it?

43:01.070 --> 43:02.670
Stay here with Old Turtle and learn from him.

43:02.670 --> 43:04.220
Contact me with this conch if anything happens.

43:04.440 --> 43:05.880
I have to stay here alone?

43:06.670 --> 43:08.110
What if the Eternal Race finds out?

43:08.110 --> 43:09.210
That's why I'm giving you this conch.

43:09.360 --> 43:10.230
Take it with you wherever you go.

43:10.230 --> 43:11.150
Don't lose it

43:11.150 --> 43:12.000
or give it to others.

43:12.000 --> 43:13.320
Otherwise, if you lose your life,

43:13.320 --> 43:14.670
don't blame me for not reminding you.

43:17.160 --> 43:18.320
There's no need to warn me.

43:18.320 --> 43:19.800
I'll teach her since you brought her here.

43:30.000 --> 43:30.870
Let's start.

43:31.360 --> 43:32.470
What do you mean start?

43:33.630 --> 43:34.880
Bow to me and take me as your master first.

43:35.990 --> 43:38.150
I, Bai Shuo, only bow to my parents, heaven and earth.

43:38.150 --> 43:40.230
I've never bowed to anyone else.

43:40.230 --> 43:41.360
If you want me to take you as my master,

43:41.360 --> 43:43.590
you have to show me your real skills first.

43:43.590 --> 43:45.880
I won't teach you if you don't bow to me.

43:45.880 --> 43:46.900
Really?

43:48.190 --> 43:49.880
Master.

43:50.710 --> 43:52.110
Go ahead.

43:52.110 --> 43:53.320
Your Highness.

43:53.320 --> 43:55.150
I'll teach you.

43:55.150 --> 43:56.550
I surrender.

43:57.450 --> 43:58.780
Nothing.

43:58.800 --> 44:00.540
I just wanted to ask

44:03.550 --> 44:04.880
if you got home safely.

44:07.630 --> 44:09.470
I'll work hard and learn from Old Turtle.

44:09.510 --> 44:10.630
When I finish my studies,

44:10.630 --> 44:12.180
remember to come and pick me up.

44:12.200 --> 44:12.880
Okay.

44:15.200 --> 44:16.280
Am I a good friend or not?

44:16.280 --> 44:17.230
I didn't tell on you.

44:20.110 --> 44:22.160
As the 1000-year-old Mystery Turtle,

44:22.180 --> 44:24.180
you must have a lot of special skills.

44:24.580 --> 44:25.420
What will you teach me first?

44:30.450 --> 44:31.820
Watch

44:31.840 --> 44:32.880
carefully.

44:49.370 --> 44:50.730
Did you get it?

44:50.760 --> 44:51.720
What?

44:52.230 --> 44:53.360
Breath holding.

44:53.730 --> 44:55.590
Are you sure this is a skill of the Eternals?

44:57.760 --> 44:58.630
My disciple.

44:58.880 --> 44:59.880
What's the most important thing

44:59.900 --> 45:01.670
in a duel?

45:01.720 --> 45:02.630
To defeat the enemy.

45:02.650 --> 45:03.610
Wrong.

45:03.640 --> 45:04.410
It's to survive.

45:04.880 --> 45:08.070
What I taught you just now is my secret technique,

45:08.100 --> 45:09.580
Turtle's Breath.

45:09.630 --> 45:10.510
But of course,

45:10.510 --> 45:12.400
you can also call it

45:13.150 --> 45:14.360
Playing Dead.

45:21.670 --> 45:22.760
I'll teach you something else.
